Wishful Drinking is an autobiographical humor book by American actress and author Carrie Fisher , published by Simon & Schuster in 2008 .
Fisher 's book was based on her one-woman stage show , which she developed with writer/director Joshua Ravetch .
The show debuted at The Geffen Playhouse with Ravetch directing .
It enjoyed a successful Broadway run and then toured in other cities .
In 2010 , HBO filmed a feature-length documentary of the stage play .